Package: claude-code-statusline
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 4.0), jq, curl, git, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: ccusage
Description: Enhanced statusline for Claude Code CLI
 A beautiful, feature-rich statusline for Claude Code with:
  - Git repository status and commit tracking
  - MCP server monitoring
  - Cost tracking and usage analytics
  - Islamic prayer times and Hijri calendar
  - Multiple themes (catppuccin, ocean, garden, classic)
  - Plugin system for custom components
  - GitHub Actions integration
 .
 Supports macOS, Ubuntu, Debian, Fedora, Arch Linux, and Alpine.
